(571, 1, '2024-06-22 21:06:56', '2024-06-22 21:06:56', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><em>🔦 Spotlight explores the impactful journeys of Diasporans excelling in their community impact, professional achievement, as well as business innovation. We uncover the challenges they’ve faced, the strategies that have led them to success, all the while providing insights, blueprints of their journeys and inspiration for all. Join us in our journey of discovering those largely under recognised heroes making hugely positive impacts on their communities and the people around them. 🔦</em></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Claudia Cholakian</strong></h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><a href=\"https://youtu.be/ureKVNEQ2LQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Watch the full interview here.</a></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Claudia Cholakian is an Australian-born football player with Armenian heritage. She has represented several clubs in the National Premier Leagues (NPL) and has played as a defender for Sydney FC in the Women\'s A-League (formerly known as the W-League). Claudia is also a current member of the Armenian national women\'s football team, which has upcoming games in 2024.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Women\'s Qualifiers Game Schedule 2024:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>May 31</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<strong>Armenia&nbsp;</strong>- Kazakhstan</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>June 4</strong>&nbsp;- Kazakhstan -&nbsp;<strong>Armenia</strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>July 12</strong>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<strong>Armenia</strong>&nbsp;- Bulgaria</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p><strong>July 16</strong>&nbsp;- Romania -&nbsp;<strong>Armenia</strong><br></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Pages to fo