heading\">Donate</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kaitzak is a not for profit entity which can take both general and specific donations. If you wish to donate to a specific organisation, please let us know and we can put in touch directly.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Donations received generally for Kaitzak will be put towards any number of projects or initiatives, such as:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>The Kaitzak Community Assurance Fund</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Volunteering, aid and assistance, both locally &amp; international</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Specific projects such as Kaitzak events, infrastructure or education initiatives</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Improving the online Kaitzak platform</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>For any donation queries please email: <strong><a href=\"mailto:hello@kaitzak.com.au\">hello@kaitzak.com.au</a></strong></p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"1px\"}},\"borderColor\":\"color-stroke\",\"backgroundColor\":\"color-header\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center has-border-color has-color-stroke-border-color has-color-header-background-color has-background\" style=\"border-width:1px;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--50)\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":911,\"aspectRatio\":\"9/16\",\"scale\":\"contain\",\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\",\"align\":\"center\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-full\"><img src=\"https://kaydzak.ankap/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/donate.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-911\" style=\"aspect-ratio:9/16;object-fit:contain\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'Contribute', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '776-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-07-06 20:20:41', '2024-07-06 20:20:41', '', 776, 'https://kaydzak.ankap/?p=944', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
(946, 1, '2024-07-06 20:23:06', '2024-07-06 20:23:06', '<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|50\"}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"justifyContent\":\"stretch\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><!-- wp:columns {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns are-vertically-aligned-center\"><!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"}},\"border\":{\"width\":\"1px\"}},\"borderColor\":\"color-stroke\",\"backgroundColor\":\"color-header\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center has-border-color has-color-stroke-border-color has-color-header-background-color has-background\" style=\"border-width:1px;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":869,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://kaydzak.ankap/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/about.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-869\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column -->\n\n<!-- wp:column {\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\",\"style\":{\"border\":{\"width\":\"1px\"},\"spacing\":{\"padding\":{\"top\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\",\"bottom\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\",\"left\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\",\"right\":\"var:preset|spacing|40\"}}},\"borderColor\":\"color-stroke\"} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center has-border-color has-color-stroke-border-color\" style=\"border-width:1px;padding-top:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-right:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-bottom:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40);padding-left:var(--wp--preset--spacing--40)\"><!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Kaitzak was founded in 2022 in Melbourne, Australia. It is a not-for-profit organised and supported by individuals who want to see our diaspora communities grow sustainably and thrive. This means looking to the strengths of our communities and helping them grow stronger.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our slogan connect, amplify, flourish summarises this notion. We connect like minded individuals, we amplify the work and messages of those who lift up those around them, and the flourishing results.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The goodwill and generosity of our communities must always be held in the highest esteem. This is the true definition of grassroots: ordinary people doing extraordinary things.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s actually pretty simple idea, but it is very powerful indeed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"margin\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:2rem\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":882,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://kaydzak.ankap/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/contributors.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-882\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contributors</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[wp_contributors]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'About Kaitzak', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-07-06 20:23:06', '2024-07-06 20:23:06', '', 41, 'https://kaydzak.ankap/?p=946', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
