h -->\n<p>Kaitzak was founded in 2022 in Melbourne, Australia. It is a not-for-profit organised and supported by individuals who want to see our diaspora communities grow sustainably and thrive. This means looking to the strengths of our communities and helping them grow stronger.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Our slogan connect, amplify, flourish summarises this notion. We connect like minded individuals, we amplify the work and messages of those who lift up those around them, and the flourishing results.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>The goodwill and generosity of our communities must always be held in the highest esteem. This is the true definition of grassroots: ordinary people doing extraordinary things.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>It’s actually pretty simple idea, but it is very powerful indeed.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph --></div>\n<!-- /wp:column --></div>\n<!-- /wp:columns -->\n\n<!-- wp:group {\"style\":{\"spacing\":{\"blockGap\":\"var:preset|spacing|30\",\"margin\":{\"top\":\"2rem\",\"bottom\":\"2rem\"}}},\"layout\":{\"type\":\"flex\",\"orientation\":\"vertical\",\"justifyContent\":\"center\",\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"}} -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\" style=\"margin-top:2rem;margin-bottom:2rem\"><!-- wp:image {\"id\":882,\"sizeSlug\":\"full\",\"linkDestination\":\"none\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img src=\"https://kaydzak.ankap/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/contributors.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-882\"/></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Contributors</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n\n<!-- wp:shortcode -->\n[wp_contributors]\n<!-- /wp:shortcode --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group --></div>\n<!-- /wp:group -->', 'About', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '41-revision-v1', '', '', '2024-08-05 17:03:37', '2024-08-05 17:03:37', '', 41, 'http://kaydzak.ankap/?p=964', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
